00:00:15.337 --> 00:00:17.813
and then just for each
dollar maximizing it.

00:00:17.813 --> 00:00:21.644
Our 1st dollar, we got 100
utility points per dollar

00:00:21.644 --> 00:00:23.142
for that first chocolate bar

00:00:23.142 --> 00:00:24.412
and that was more than any

00:00:24.412 --> 00:00:25.791
than the first fruits,

00:00:25.791 --> 00:00:27.001
